  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we spoke Russian by that time, because we spent-- while I was going to school in the Ukraine, so-- we finally got back to Belovodsk, and we found out that my mother and my brother and sister-in-law were sent to a collective farm in Belovodsk.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we looked them up, and when we got there-- and my sister got sick.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She got, I think it was typhus, from all the dirt and all that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she got deathly sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got an assignment to work on the collective farm, drive a pair of-- a wagon with a pair of horses-- to deliver the wheat from one end to the town.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we-- we were able to survive, literally, from the-- from what they gave us on the collective farm.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Plus, as I was driving the team of horses with wheat, I would tie up my bottoms of my pants and pour the-- as I was driving, pour the wheat into my pants to fill up the pants.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I would drive by the little cabin that we stayed in and jump off and undo the bottoms of the pants, and we would accumulate wheat that way.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "By that time we were informed that the Polish government in London--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1940, '41, '42, somewhere in-- because by that time, was all summer already, so I don't know seasons, exactly.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the Polish government and London had an agreement with the Soviet Union to form a Polish army, the Anders army, A-N-D-E-R-S.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because of that, they became very lenient with our people.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
